chapter:
&reftitle.setup;
&reftitle.required;
Dependencies:
libgetdns 0.3.0
getdns library header files
The configure script used to build the extension will confirm that the dependencies have been met.
&reftitle.install;
The getdns extension is built and installed from a *NIX command shell. Run the following commands to build and install the extension:
$ phpize $ ./configure --enable-getdns $ make $ sudo make install
Run the following commands to clean the build directory:
$ make clean $ phpize --clean
The getdns library and associated PHP language bindings are not currently available for Microsoft Windows.
&reftitle.runtime;
There are currently no configuration options available. All functional parameters are set using the 'set' and 'get' functions.
&reftitle.resources;
The getdns extension has no resource types defined.
